You must have the fifamanager image emulated by Daemon Tools or Alcohool or copied in a DVD disc. 

1. Extract all the content to C:\FIFAMANAGER11 (example - can be any other)

2.Move and overwrite all the content downloaded from this torrent to C:\FIFAMANAGER11

3.Disconect from the internet and disable antivirus for this moment (you can activate after)

4. Run EAsetup 

5. When it asks for the serial, in the background (alt+TAB) run the file ACTIVATION.exe

6. Proceed with the install.

7. Run Fifa Manager 11

8. You can enable antivirus an internet for now.

p.s.: I had no problems at all...game is running flawlessly.

1. From the game image, extract all files to your C:\fifamanager11 (eg)

2. Disconnect from the internet and move all the files from this torrent to your C:\fifamanager11   Overwrite it

3. Run antorun.exe or setup (the key will be generated and will start the installation)

4. Remember your AV have to be off. When you turn on it might move activation.exe to guarantine and you have to restore it to run the game again.

5. IT WORKS! People that have not been successful is doing something wrong!
